---
const dashboardImg = "/educational_dashboard_app_1778817181108.png";
const classroomImg = "/kids_studying_together_1778817129229.png";
---

<section class="py-32 px-6 bg-[#F8FAFC] relative overflow-hidden border-t border-slate-100">
  <!-- Glowing Aurora Orbs (Soft Light Accent) -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-[#6320EE]/5 blur-[120px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-[350px] h-[350px] bg-[#C6F432]/5 blur-[110px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-24">
      <span class="text-[#6320EE] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs mb-4 block">Layanan Populer</span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-slate-900 leading-tight">
        Kenapa Harus <span class="text-[#6320EE] underline decoration-[#C6F432] underline-offset-8">LENTERA ?</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature 1: Image Left -->
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-20 mb-40">
      <div class="flex-1 relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#6320EE]/10 blur-[80px] rounded-full"></div>
        <div class="relative p-4 bg-[#6320EE] rounded-[4rem] rotate-[-3deg] shadow-2xl">
          <img src={classroomImg} alt="Session" class="w-full h-[450px] object-cover rounded-[3.5rem]" />
          <div class="absolute top-10 -left-10 bg-white border border-slate-100 p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl max-w-[200px] hidden lg:block animate-pulse">
            <p class="text-slate-900 font-bold text-sm">Belajar Asyik dengan bantuan AI 🚀</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-8 leading-tight uppercase tracking-tighter">Materi yang DI sajikan akan beradaptasi Dengan Kemampuan Kamu</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-lg mb-10 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          Kamu tidak akan merasa tertekan karena harus mengejar temanmu, kamu juga tidak akan merasa bosan karena materi yang disajikan akan sesuai dengan kemampuan kamu.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          {["Pilihan Jadwal Fleksibel", "Materi Adaptif", "Laporan Progres Real-time"].map(item => (
            <li class="flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-600 font-bold">
              <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-[#6320EE] text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-black">✓</span>
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature 2: Image Right -->
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-20">
      <div class="flex-1 relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-amber-500/10 blur-[80px] rounded-full"></div>
        <div class="relative p-4 bg-[#F59E0B] rounded-[4rem] rotate-[3deg] shadow-2xl">
          <img src={dashboardImg} alt="Pace" class="w-full h-[450px] object-cover rounded-[3.5rem]" />
          <div class="absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 bg-white border border-slate-100 p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl max-w-[220px] hidden lg:block">
            <p class="text-slate-900 font-bold text-sm">Pace Belajar: Optimal ⚡</p>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-2">Berdasarkan gaya belajarmu minggu ini.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-8 leading-tight uppercase tracking-tighter">Mudah Untuk Di Akses Kapan Saja & Di Mana Saja</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-lg mb-10 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          Tidak peduli di mana kamu berada atau jam berapa sekarang, LENTERA selalu siap membantumu belajar. Akses kapan saja, di mana saja.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="p-8 bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500">
            <span class="text-3xl mb-4 block">⚡</span>
            <p class="text-slate-900 font-black uppercase text-sm mb-2">Fast Lane</p>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs leading-relaxed font-medium">Untuk topik yang sudah kamu kuasai sepenuhnya.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500">
            <span class="text-3xl mb-4 block">🐢</span>
            <p class="text-slate-900 font-black uppercase text-sm mb-2">Deep Dive</p>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs leading-relaxed font-medium">Sabar di materi yang memang menantang.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
